s1397: Qi King Han Xin transferred to Chu King.
s1399: Attached to Han, became Nanhai commandery.
s1403: Twelfth. Transferred king to Chu, attached to Han, became four commanderies.
s1406: First month. Killed Xiang Ji, world pacified, lords became subjects of Han.
s1410: Fifth year, first month. Yan kingdom.
s1414: Fourth. Han King Xin transferred to Dai king, capital at Mayi.
s1415: Divided Linjiang to form Changsha kingdom.
s1427: Second month. Jiawu day, king changed title, took emperor position at Dingtao.
s1436: Hengshan King Wu Rui became Changsha King.
